| männlich oft der | -e oft die | -chen immer das |', null, null, null, 1, true, '{"kind":"article_help","content_md":{"de":"# Artikel immer mit dem Wort lernen\nLerne nicht nur **Hund**, sondern immer **der Hund**. Der Artikel gehört zum Wort.\n\n| der Hund | die Katze | das Haus |\n| männlich oft der | -e oft die | -chen immer das |","en":"# Learn the article with the word\nDo not learn only **Hund**. Learn **der Hund**. The article belongs to the noun.\n\n| der Hund | die Katze | das Haus |\n| often masculine | -e often die | -chen always das |"},"lesson_slug":"de-a1-basics-articles","learn_language":"de"}'::jsonb),
  ('44959747-7f8f-53e5-81ac-08233e8edd21', 'de-a1-articles-hund', 'vocabulary', 'der Hund', 'der hunt', 'noun', 'Der Hund ist klein.', null, 'de-a1-articles', 'beginner', null, 'https://pqnfiqczcxnwaenylysb.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/language-cards/audio/de-a1/basics-articles-20260705152000/de-a1-articles-hund.mp3', null, 'b5d6c86e-3922-430b-897d-907ed060a047', 11, true, '{"hint":{"de":"Viele Tiere mit männlicher Form nehmen der. Wichtig: der Hund.","en":"Many animals with a male form use der. Key pair: der Hund."},"kind":"article_noun","noun":"Hund","article":"der","english":"dog","lesson_slug":"de-a1-basics-articles","learn_language":"de"}'::jsonb),
  ('d789e544-60b2-5d1d-9506-d03d6e3d652a', 'de-a1-articles-tisch', 'vocabulary', 'der Tisch', 'der tisch', 'noun', 'Der Tisch ist groß.', null, 'de-a1-articles', 'beginner', null, 'https://pqnfiqczcxnwaenylysb.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/language-cards/audio/de-a1/basics-articles-20260705152000/de-a1-articles-tisch.mp3', null, '540c31f2-d763-4c93-b6d0-0b4eee94b0b1', 12, true, '{"hint":{"de":"Tisch hat keine sichere Endung. Lerne es als festes Paar: der Tisch.","en":"Tisch has no safe ending rule. Learn it as a fixed pair: der Tisch."},"kind":"article_noun","noun":"Tisch","article":"der","english":"table","lesson_slug":"de-a1-basics-articles","learn_language":"de"}'::jsonb),
  ('4d4314ab-a6cd-5c29-98e4-e04dcdca581b', 'de-a1-articles-zug', 'vocabulary', 'der Zug', 'der tsook', 'noun', 'Der Zug kommt.', null, 'de-a1-articles', 'beginner', null, 'https://pqnfiqczcxnwaenylysb.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/language-cards/audio/de-a1/basics-articles-20260705152000/de-a1-articles-zug.mp3', null, '56121670-e684-47fc-9b13-b6e1572e8344', 13, true, '{"hint":{"de":"Zug hat keine sichere Endung. Für A1 fest merken: der Zug.","en":"Zug has no safe ending rule. For A1, memorize the pair: der Zug."},"kind":"article_noun","noun":"Zug","article":"der","english":"train","lesson_slug":"de-a1-basics-articles","learn_language":"de"}'::jsonb),
  ('7cd5b995-52f5-51dc-81a6-0d25e6ac2711', 'de-a1-articles-schluessel', 'vocabulary', 'der Schlüssel', 'der SHLÜS-sel', 'noun', 'Der Schlüssel ist hier.', null, 'de-a1-articles', 'beginner', null, 'https://pqnfiqczcxnwaenylysb.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/language-cards/audio/de-a1/basics-articles-20260705152000/de-a1-articles-schluessel.mp3', null, '1a7c7a3f-9efb-4b03-8518-5fda94814e16', 14, true, '{"hint":{"de":"Wörter auf -el sind sehr oft der: der Schlüssel.","en":"Words ending in -el are very often der: der Schlüssel."},"kind":"article_noun","noun":"Schlüssel","article":"der","english":"key","lesson_slug":"de-a1-basics-articles","learn_language":"de"}'::jsonb),
  ('b6383b12-e5ef-5660-a988-129804655ca0', 'de-a1-articles-loeffel', 'vocabulary', 'der Löffel', 'der LÖF-fel', 'noun', 'Der Löffel ist klein.', null, 'de-a1-articles', 'beginner', null, 'https://pqnfiqczcxnwaenylysb.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/language-cards/audio/de-a1/basics-articles-20260705152000/de-a1-articles-loeffel.mp3', null, '5a12cfe2-8ed5-4bee-9036-4a5771e865b9', 15, true, '{"hint":{"de":"Auch -el: der Löffel. Schlüssel und Löffel teilen der.","en":"Another -el word: der Löffel. Schlüssel and Löffel both use der."},"kind":"article_noun","noun":"Löffel","article":"der","english":"spoon","lesson_slug":"de-a1-basics-articles","learn_language":"de"}'::jsonb),
  ('798e0fbd-06b5-54f4-b94f-30cc141df22c', 'de-a1-articles-stuhl', 'vocabulary', 'der Stuhl', 'der shtool', 'noun', 'Der Stuhl ist frei.', null, 'de-a1-articles', 'beginner', null, 'https://pqnfiqczcxnwaenylysb.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/language-cards/audio/de-a1/basics-articles-articles-expanded-20260705/de-a1-articles-stuhl.mp3', null, '9b669beb-d285-4159-b6dd-528e9e239406', 16, true, '{"hint":{"de":"Stuhl ist ein Alltagswort ohne Regel. Als festes Paar lernen: der Stuhl.","en":"Stuhl has no safe ending rule. Learn it as a fixed pair: der Stuhl."},"kind":"article_noun","noun":"Stuhl","article":"der","english":"chair","lesson_slug":"de-a1-basics-articles","learn_language":"de"}'::jsonb),
  ('1ce5685a-e1ab-558a-aacd-df2568bcdf62', 'de-a1-articles-help-der', 'info', 'Wann oft der?', null, null, null, null, 'de-a1-articles', 'beginner', '# Wann oft der?
**der** ist häufig bei männlichen Personen und Tieren. Einige Endungen helfen auch.

- oft männlich: **der Mann**, **der Hund**
- oft -er: **der Computer**
- oft -el: **der Schlüssel**, **der Löffel**', null, null, null, 7, true, '{"kind":"article_help","content_md":{"de":"# Wann oft der?\n**der** ist häufig bei männlichen Personen und Tieren. Einige Endungen helfen auch.\n\n- oft männlich: **der Mann**, **der Hund**\n- oft -er: **der Computer**\n- oft -el: **der Schlüssel**, **der Löffel**","en":"# When is it often der?\n**der** is common for male people and animals. Some endings also help.\n\n- often male: **der Mann**, **der Hund**\n- often -er: **der Computer**\n- often -el: **der Schlüssel**, **der Löffel**"},"lesson_slug":"de-a1-basics-articles","learn_language":"de"}'::jsonb),
  ('8b2880f6-4285-5d67-8897-3cae2204f117', 'de-a1-articles-ball', 'vocabulary', 'der Ball', 'der bal', 'noun', 'Der Ball ist rund.', null, 'de-a1-articles', 'beginner', null, 'https://pqnfiqczcxnwaenylysb.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/language-cards/audio/de-a1/basics-articles-articles-expanded-20260705/de-a1-articles-ball.mp3', null, '4c2bafd6-309a-4af9-b050-a269bd039cca', 17, true, '{"hint":{"de":"Viele kurze Gegenstände sind nicht automatisch der, aber Ball ist es: der Ball.","en":"Short object words are not always der, but Ball is: der Ball."},"kind":"article_noun","noun":"Ball","article":"der","english":"ball","lesson_slug":"de-a1-basics-articles","learn_language":"de"}'::jsonb),
  ('d655fd9c-ecf7-528b-a7e6-76991cffd6a2', 'de-a1-articles-schuh', 'vocabulary', 'der Schuh', 'der shoo', 'noun', 'Der Schuh ist schwarz.', null, 'de-a1-articles', 'beginner', null, 'https://pqnfiqczcxnwaenylysb.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/language-cards/audio/de-a1/basics-articles-articles-expanded-20260705/de-a1-articles-schuh.mp3', null, '5e72d19d-c0ab-4423-a131-ea1959deb952', 18, true, '{"hint":{"de":"Kleidung hat keinen sicheren Artikel. Merke als Paar: der Schuh.","en":"Clothing has no safe article rule. Learn the pair: der Schuh."},"kind":"article_noun","noun":"Schuh","article":"der","english":"shoe","lesson_slug":"de-a1-basics-articles","learn_language":"de"}'::jsonb),
  ('8c2650cc-2539-510a-9370-b7b93223368c', 'de-a1-articles-park', 'vocabulary', 'der Park', 'der park', 'noun', 'Der Park ist grün.', null, 'de-a1-articles', 'beginner', null, 'https://pqnfiqczcxnwaenylysb.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/language-cards/audio/de-a1/basics-articles-articles-expanded-20260705/de-a1-articles-park.mp3', null, 'c496e591-dba1-45cd-96d4-847b336a3c2b', 19, true, '{"hint":{"de":"Viele Orte mit kurzer, harter Form sind der. Für A1: der Park.","en":"Many short place words use der. For A1, remember: der Park."},"kind":"article_noun","noun":"Park","article":"der","english":"park","lesson_slug":"de-a1-basics-articles","learn_language":"de"}'::jsonb),
